reviewText: ordered it for my sister who found this video very helpful.

This was not an interview of the usual "broadcast TV"  quality, however all I wanted to know was available to me in this DVD set. If any of you marveled at the writing behind Showtime's "Weeds" series as I have, and would like to know more about how it came about, I recommend this two disc DVD interview with the screenwriter Jenji Kohan.
